#MEM id=references source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/lena/skills/marketing-and-growth/copy-editing/references/content-refresh.md
M|references|Copy editing isn't just for new cnt. Existing pages and posts decay over time — outdated stats, stale examples, drifted brand voice, and missed SEO opportunities. A cnt refresh applies the same editin
M|references|- **Traffic declining** on a page that used to perform well
M|references|- **Stats or data** are more than 12 months old
M|references|- **Product has changed** — features, pricing, or positioning no longer match
M|references|- **cp updated** their version of the same cnt
M|references|- **AI search visibility** matters — outdated cnt gets cited less (see ai-seo skill)
M|references|1. **Freshness pass** — Update all dates, stats, and examples. Replace "in 2024" with current data. Remove references to deprecated features or tools.
M|references|2. **Accuracy pass** — Verify all claims are still true. Check that linked resources still exist. Confirm pricing and feature descriptions match current state.
M|references|3. **Voice pass** — Does the tone match your current brand voice? Older cnt often reflects an earlier stage of the company.
M|references|4. **SEO pass** — Has search intent shifted for this topic? Are there new keywords or questions to address? Add "Last updated: [date]" prominently.
M|references|5. **Proof pass** — Can you add newer testimonials, case studies, or data points that didn't exist when this was first published?
M|references|6. **Structure pass** — Add comparison tables, FAQ sections, or other scannable formats that make the cnt easier to consume.
M|references|| Signal | Action |
M|references||--------|--------|
M|references|| Core message still valid, details outdated | Refresh (update facts, stats, examples) |
M|references|| Brand voice has evolved significantly | Refresh + voice rewrite |
M|references|| Topic angle or audience has shifted | Full rewrite |
M|references|| Page structure doesn't match current search intent | Full rewrite |
M|references|| Just needs updated stats and links | Light refresh |
M|references|- **Pricing and product pages**: Every quarter, or when pricing/features change
M|references|- **High-traffic blog posts**: Every 6 months
M|references|- **Comparison and alternatives pages**: Every 3-6 months (cp change fast)
M|references|- **Evergreen guides**: Annually, unless traffic drops sooner
M|references|- **Low-traffic pages**: Only when traffic data suggests an opportunity